	//{"129", "<div id=\"mw-content-text\" class=\"mw-body-content\"><div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"zh-Hans-CN\" dir=\"ltr\"><figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:GaussianBeamWaist.svg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/53/GaussianBeamWaist.svg/350px-GaussianBeamWaist.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"350\" height=\"170\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/53/GaussianBeamWaist.svg/525px-GaussianBeamWaist.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/53/GaussianBeamWaist.svg/700px-GaussianBeamWaist.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"416\" data-file-height=\"202\"></a><figcaption>高斯光束的宽度<span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle w(z)}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mi>w</mi>\n        <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n        <mi>z</mi>\n        <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle w(z)}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/13626102fd9be0d15ff137c157c1aed6caf339a0\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:4.562ex; height:2.843ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle w(z)}\"></span>是轴向距离<span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle z}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mi>z</mi>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle z}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/bf368e72c009decd9b6686ee84a375632e11de98\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.088ex; height:1.676ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle z}\"></span>、射束腰部 <span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle w_{0}}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <msub>\n          <mi>w</mi>\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </msub>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle w_{0}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/7aa052386ec49846179aa8bbe2b279b57a675e00\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.718ex; height:2.009ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle w_{0}}\"></span>、共焦参数<span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle b}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mi>b</mi>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle b}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/f11423fbb2e967f986e36804a8ae4271734917c3\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:0.998ex; height:2.176ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle b}\"></span>、瑞利距离<span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle z_{\\mathrm {R} }}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <msub>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n              <mi mathvariant=\"normal\">R</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mrow>\n        </msub>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle z_{\\mathrm {R} }}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/5cc1f1605248e6a63ce87b19b4d725aa6a21c908\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:2.523ex; height:2.009ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle z_{\\mathrm {R} }}\"></span>及总角度分布<span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle \\Theta }\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Θ<!-- Θ --></mi>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle \\Theta }</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/bc927b19f46d005b4720db7a0f96cd5b6f1a0d9b\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.808ex; height:2.176ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle \\Theta }\"></span>的函数</figcaption></figure>\n<p>在<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"光学\">光学</a>及<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8\" title=\"激光科学\">激光科学</a>中，<b>瑞利距离</b>或<b>瑞利长度</b>（Rayleigh length）或<b>瑞利范围</b>（Rayleigh range）是指<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%85%89%E6%9D%9F\" title=\"光束\">光束</a>沿着其行进方向，从其<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%B0%84%E6%9D%9F%E8%85%B0%E9%83%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"射束腰部\">腰部</a>到其面积为腰部面积两倍的<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%88%AA%E9%9D%A2_(%E5%B9%BE%E4%BD%95)\" title=\"截面 (几何)\">截面</a>的距离<sup id=\"cite_ref-Siegman1986_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Siegman1986-1\" title=\"\">[1]</a></sup>，此时截面半径约为<span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\displaystyle {\\sqrt {2}}}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <msqrt>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msqrt>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle {\\sqrt {2}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/b4afc1e27d418021bf10898eb44a7f5f315735ff\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.671ex; width:3.098ex; height:3.009ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle {\\sqrt {2}}}\"></span> 倍的腰部半径。另一个相关的参数为<b>共焦参数</b>（confocal parameter）<i>b</i>，恰为瑞利距离的两倍<sup id=\"cite_ref-Damask_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Damask-2\">[2]</a></sup>。当用<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%AB%98%E6%96%AF%E5%85%89%E6%9D%9F\" title=\"高斯光束\">高斯光束</a>来做为光束模型时，瑞利距离是相当重要的参数。\n</p></div>\n</div>", "![](//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/53/GaussianBeamWaist.svg)\n高斯光束的宽度 ${\\displaystyle w(z)}$ 是轴向距离 ${\\displaystyle z}$、射束腰部 ${\\displaystyle w_{0}}$、共焦参数 ${\\displaystyle b}$、瑞利距离 ${\\displaystyle z_{\\mathrm {R} }}$ 及总角度分布 ${\\displaystyle \\Theta }$ 的函数\n\n\n在[光学](/wiki/%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8 \"光学\")及[激光科学](/wiki/%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8 \"激光科学\")中，**瑞利距离**或\u200b**瑞利长度**\u200b（Rayleigh length）或\u200b**瑞利范围**\u200b（Rayleigh range）是指[光束](/wiki/%E5%85%89%E6%9D%9F \"光束\")沿着其行进方向，从其[腰部](/wiki/%E5%B0%84%E6%9D%9F%E8%85%B0%E9%83%A8 \"射束腰部\")到其面积为腰部面积两倍的[截面](/wiki/%E6%88%AA%E9%9D%A2_(%E5%B9%BE%E4%BD%95) \"截面 (几何)\")的距离\u200b^[[1]](#cite_note-Siegman1986-1)^\u200b，此时截面半径约为 ${\\displaystyle {\\sqrt {2}}}$ 倍的腰部半径。另一个相关的参数为\u200b**共焦参数**\u200b（confocal parameter）\u200b*b*\u200b，恰为瑞利距离的两倍\u200b^[[2]](#cite_note-Damask-2)^\u200b。当用[高斯光束](/wiki/%E9%AB%98%E6%96%AF%E5%85%89%E6%9D%9F \"高斯光束\")来做为光束模型时，瑞利距离是相当重要的参数。\n"},
